---
description: Testing standards and requirements
globs:
  - "tests/**"
  - "ui/src/**/*.test.*"
  - "ui/e2e/**"
---

- C tests: every new function needs at least one test; test names follow `subject_expected_behavior`
- C tests: use `SC_IS_TEST` guards for side effects; no real network, no process spawning
- UI component tests: every `sc-*` component must have tests in `components.test.ts` or `extra-components.test.ts`
- UI tests: test custom element registration, property reflection, default state, ARIA attributes
- E2E tests: include axe-core accessibility checks for every page/view
- Never assert `SC_ASSERT_TRUE(1)` or tautological conditions — use meaningful assertions
- Free all allocations in C tests — ASan catches leaks
